<template lang="pug">
.v-swiper(class='swiper-container' :id='name')
  .swiper-wrapper
    .swiper-slide(v-for="item in list")
      slot(:info="item")
  .swiper-pagination(v-if="page")
  .swiper-button-prev(v-if="btn")
  .swiper-button-next(v-if="btn")
</template>

<script>
export default {
	name: 'v-swiper',
	components: {},
	props: {
		name: String,
		list: Array,
		speed: {
			type: Number,
			default: 400,
		},
		autoplay: {
			type: Object,
			default() {
				return { disableOnInteraction: false, delay: 3000 }
			},
		},
		page: {
			type: Boolean,
			default: false,
		},
		slidesPerView: {
			type: Number,
			default: 4,
		},
		spaceBetween: {
			type: Number,
			default: 30,
		},
		btn: {
			type: Boolean,
			default: true,
		},
	},
	data() {
		return {}
	},
	computed: {},
	methods: {},
	mounted() {
		var clientWidth = parseInt(window.innerWidth)
		new Swiper(`#${this.name}`, {
			loop: true,
			speed: this.speed,
			autoplay: this.autoplay,
			pagination: {
				el: this.page ? '.swiper-pagination' : '',
			},
			navigation: this.btn
				? {
						nextEl: '.swiper-button-next',
						prevEl: '.swiper-button-prev',
				  }
				: '',
			slidesPerView: clientWidth < 800 ? 1 : this.slidesPerView,
			spaceBetween: this.spaceBetween,
		})
	},
}
</script>
